title: 'Gimme Shelter': Newsom falls far short on his big housing promises
dc:creator: Liam Dillon
description: At the end of his first term in office, Gov. Gavin Newsom has not met his major promises to build a lot more homes and ease California's housing crisis.
content:encoded: At the end of his first term in office, Gov. Gavin Newsom has not met his major promises to build a lot more homes and ease California's housing crisis.
